### 搭建环境
 * ubuntu
 -> sudo apt update
 -> apt install -y cmake pkg-config libssl-dev git build-essential clang libclang-dev curl
 
 * rust 安装
 -> # Install
    curl https://sh.rustup.rs -sSf | sh
    # Configure
    source ~/.cargo/env
 ->  Clone the Node Template (version v2.0.0).
   * git clone -b v2.0.0 --depth 1 https://github.com/substrate-developer-hub/substrate-node-template
   * make init
   * make build
 -> git clone -b v2.0.0 --depth 1 https://github.com/substrate-developer-hub/substrate-front-end-template
   * yarn install

### 问题
安装node 
# Using Ubuntu
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_12.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

# Using Debian, as root
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_12.x | bash -
apt-get install -y nodejs

安装 yarn
全局安装 npm install -g yarn 默认1.22   

libusb.1.0.sp 找不到问题 
 * git clone https://github.com/libusb/libusb.git  apt install autoconf automake libtool-bin libudev-dev libusb-dev 
 * ./configure && make && make install
 * 转:https://blog.csdn.net/liuzq/article/details/103614730
 
 
ws 链接问题
修改 substrate-front-end-template/src/development.json 配置 链接地址

安装 nginx 
dnf info nginx / dnf install nginx 




 

